{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "an effeet juhs gan Namnuß us-\naifftichi no zirſteein Akmiceem/\net juhs eekſch teem ne dſihwo-\neet/ juhs effat diſchannuś Wiḥ-\nna-Dahrsus ſtahdtiſchi/ bet wiṇ-\nko Wiḥnu juhs ne dſerfeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo es ſimu / ka juhfo\nPahrkahpschann dands/un juh-\nu Grehku warren dands irraid:\nTee nospaida to Taṭṭnu/un jeṁ\nSalihdsinaſchanaß Naudu/un\natmett tohs Waijadſignuś eekſch\nWahrtim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht zeetihs tas Sa-\nprattigs tanni Laiká kluſu / jo\ntas buhs weens nikus Laiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Meklejeet to Labbu / un\nne to Launu / ka juhs dſihwo-\njat/ un ta buhs tas KUNGS\ntas Deews Zebaot ar jums/ ka\njuhs fakkat.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Eenihſteet to Launu / un\nmihtejeet to Labbu/ un eezeleeet\nto Teefu eekſch Wahrtin/ jaſchu\ntas KUNGS tas Deews Zeba-\not apſchehloſees pahr Jahſepa\nAtliktſcheim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tadeht ta faeka tas\nKUNGS / tas Deews Zebaot/\ntas Klings: Wiṣṣas Eeläs buhs\nSchehloſchana/ un wiṣṣas Sat-\nwês taps faazzihts / waj! waj!\nun tee fanfs to Arraju pee Beh-\ndafchanaß/un Randafchana buhs\npee teem/ kas mahk waideht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir wiṣṣas Wiḥna-Dahr-\nfös buhs Schehloſchana / jo es\neeſchu zaar juhto Widdu / faeka\ntas KUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wajteem! faṣ ta KUR-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Itt ka' weens behgtu\npreekſch weena Lauwa / un tam\nfaſtapту weens Lahtis. Jeb kad\nweens kahtä Namnuä nahktu/\nun atſleeſohs ar jawas Rohkas\npee Seenas/ un weena Tchuhſ-\nka winnu eedſeltu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Neggi tad ta KUNGA\nDeena buhs Tumſiba/ un ne\nGaisma/ un Krehfiba / ta ka\nSpohſchums pee tahs ne effus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Es eenihſtu un atmettu\njuhtu Swehtkus/ un ne gribbu\njuhfäs Sasauſchanaß Deenäs\nohſchnaht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jo jevfchu juhs man\nDedsamo-Uppurus uppurejat /\nuhdſ ar juhſeim Ehdamo-Uppu-\nreem / tad tomehr man ne irr\nlabs Brahts pee winneem/ ir to\nPateikſchanaß-Uppurt no juh-\nſeim Taukeem es ne gribbu uſ-\nskattiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Atjenuu tikcai no man-\nnim to Btautchanu tawo Dſeſ-\nmu/ ir tawo Rehtlu Slannu es\nne gribbu dsirdeht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet ta Teefa tezzehs ka\nUhdens/ un ta Taifniba ka ſtip-\nra Uppe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Effat juhs man tſchetr-\ndefſimits Gaddus Tuſfnefi Up-\npurus / un Ehdamo-Uppurus\npeeneAufcht? at Iſraeta Nams!\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhs gan neſſatto Buh-\non juhsa Rehuina/un to Kinny\nDoo juh-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
